      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1762139131590,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data Model\n    Tables- Collections of related data.\n     Items- Individual records,each with a unique \nPrimary  Key (Like rows in a spreadsheet)\n    Attributes-The actual data fields within \neach item eg. name , age",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Data Model\n    Tables- Collections of related data.\n     Items- Individual records,each with a unique \nPrimary  Key (Like rows in a spreadsheet)\n    Attributes-The actual data fields within \neach item eg. name , age",
