      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1762225634407,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Complex query patterns -DDB not optimized for complex joins & subquries\n2. Multi-part transactions -- DDB has limit on number of items\n3. Data model complexity -- lots of GSI and LSIs",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Complex query patterns -DDB not optimized for complex joins & subquries\n2. Multi-part transactions -- DDB has limit on number of items\n3. Data model complexity -- lots of GSI and LSIs",
